      • setSamplingMethod

        public void setSamplingMethod(org.aksw.mex.util.MEXEnum.EnumSamplingMethods sm,
                              java.lang.Double train,
                              java.lang.Double test)
                       throws java.lang.Exception
        Set the Sampling Method for a given Experiment Configuration. There is an automatic counter in order to deal with more the 1 experiment configuration grouped in 1 experiment, i.e., We would have (for instance) 2 Sampling Methods instances at the same model. Therefore, different id's are required.
        Parameters:
